@startuml 时序图-相似梦境匹配
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

title 时序图：相似梦境匹配

actor 用户 as User
participant "InterpretationController" as Controller
participant "SimilarDreamService" as Service
participant "TagService" as TagSvc
participant "Dream" as Dream
database "数据库" as DB

User -> Controller: 选择梦境，点击「相似梦境」
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: findSimilarDreams(dreamId)
activate Service

Service -> DB: 查询当前梦境及标签
DB --> Service: Dream + List<Tag>

Service -> TagSvc: getRecommendedTags()
activate TagSvc
TagSvc -> DB: 查询标签
DB --> TagSvc: 标签列表
TagSvc --> Service: List<Tag>
deactivate TagSvc

Service -> DB: 查询已分享的梦境（含标签）
DB --> Service: List<SharedDream>

loop 遍历每个已分享梦境
  Service -> Service: calculateSimilarity(当前梦境, 候选梦境)
  note right: 基于标签重叠度、关键词相似度计算
end

Service -> Service: 按相似度排序，取Top N

Service --> Controller: List<SharedDream>（匿名处理）
deactivate Service

Controller --> User: 展示相似梦境列表
deactivate Controller

@enduml
